                    <span>This is a good book for all those who are guided to find out more about Buddhism without most of the one-sided different sects. Thats one reason I liked it. Also the history,dates,times. Pictures are a plus in here. This was one of the 3 or 4th books I read that changed my mind on becoming a Buddhist.Clear,precise. Beside the Dalai Lamas books I recommend this to others searching.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">What  the Buddha is said to have taught</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
